\c 4
\s Mufaro nerugre zviri kuna Jehovha
\d kumutungamiriri wenziyo; nemitengeramwa.Pisarema raDhavhidhi.
\p
\v 1 Ndipindurei kana ndichidana,Mwari wokururama kwangu;Pakumanikidzwa kwangu makandiisa pakafarikana;ndinzwirei tsitsi, munzwe munyengetero wangu.
\v 2 Nhai vanakomana vavanhu kukudzwa kwangu kuchashandurwa kunyadziswa kusvikira rinhiko? Muchada zvisina maturo , nekutsvaka nhema kusvikira rinhi?
\v 3 Asi zivai kuti Jehovha akazvitsaurira munhu ,anomuda Jehovha uchanzwa kana ndichidana kwaari.
\v 4 Ityai murege kutadza; Tauriranai nemoyo yenyu panhovo dzenyu,muti mwii.
\v 5 Bayirai zvibayiro zvokururama, muvimbe naJehovha
\v 6 Vazhinji variko vanoti,"Ndianiko achatiratidza zvakanaka? Jehovha simudzirai pamusoro pedu chiedza chechiso chenyu."
\v 7 makaisa mufaro mumoyo mangu,Unopfuura wavanhu kana zviyo zvavo newaini yavo zvawanzwa.
\v 8 ndichavata pasi nerugare, ndibatwe nehope; Nokuti ndimi moga Jehovha munondigarisa pakasimba.
